### Installation
``` bash
$ git clone https://github.com/wlsgur11/2025_PNU_Bootcamp.git
$ cd 2025_PNU_Bootcamp
```
#### Backend
```CMD
// open CMD (sure not powershell in window os)
$ venv\Scripts\activate.bat
$ (venv) fastapi dev main.py
```

#### Frontend
```powershell
Different terminal with backend
$ cd FrontEnd
$ cd frontend
$ npm install 
$ npm run dev
```
